 and is very brave to try and make his story heard around the world. Highly recommended!","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/37439004?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1262829331"},"likeCount":124,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":88,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:2752994":{"id":2752994,"__typename":"User","legacyId":2752994,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1552868566i/2752994._UX200_CR0,7,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1135,"viewableName":"Dem","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/2752994-dem","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":986},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.hxbfNOj56_6lwqc5L4Rf8g":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.hxbfNOj56_6lwqc5L4Rf8g","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.LL5qk5FVzK228GPDb7ro8w"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:2752994"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1644103813393,"createdAt":1515924177700,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1516359760324,"text":"\u003cb\u003eNow this is an \u003cu\u003e explosive, revealing \u003c/u\u003eand \u003cu\u003e shocking\u003c/u\u003e read that had my complete attention from page one. Bill Browder's account reads like a thriller but its non fiction and is compelling reading for anyone interested in reading about High Finance, Murder and one man's fight for justice in modern Russia.\u003c/b\u003e \u003cbr\u003eimage: \u003cimg src=\"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1516321297i/24891469.jpg\" width=\"150\" height='200\"\u0026lt;br' class=\"gr-hostedUserImg\" loading=\"lazy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cb\u003e\n  \u003ci\u003e November 2009 an emancipated young lawyer, 